        {
            "id": 6324187,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電站上1800元 光通訊、生技、航運齊揚 衝破32700點創新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股標普、<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>、<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那指</a>持續走強，台股今 (28) 日延續多頭行情，以 32381.76 點開出，上漲 63.84 點，而在台積電上漲 20 元，攻上 1800 元大關，以及光通訊、生技、散裝航運同步走強，最高來到 32706.72 點，上漲近三百點，創下盤中新高點。早盤估量 11255 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6324187/l/6407c58a1991efb1513c900252e1079b.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉台積電站上1800元 光通訊、生技、航運齊揚 衝破32700點創盤中新高。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股漲多於跌，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 上漲 20 元，來到 1800 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 下跌 5 元，鴻海（2317）漲約 1%；廣達（2382）上漲 0.5 元；台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 持平。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光通訊族群延續前一日行情，光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>) 跳空漲停，波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)、眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>) 同樣攻上漲停板，聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>) 漲逾 8%，華星光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>) 漲逾 6%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>印度與泰國傳出高致死率立百病毒，資金湧入生技股，毛寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1732:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1732\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1732-TW</a>)、康那香 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9919-TW</a>)、亞諾法 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4133:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4133\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4133-TW</a>) 攻上漲停板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>散裝航運中小型船日租金向上，散裝航運股走揚，新興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2605-TW</a>)、裕民 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2606:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2606\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2606-TW</a>)、中航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2612:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2612\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2612-TW</a>) 攻上漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
